.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但地鐵收得順<br />\n利申: 人仔轉SMT"},{"pid":"b54a3c07ef38948134c8b24c9dbfcef273ad387e","tid":184752,"uid":20670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不嬲都知冇450，佢冇寫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算收爆格都係得1xmb 有無咁誇<br />\n之前人仔4g都快過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果人仔唔係成日地鐵load空氣嘅話，都真心快過SMT<br />\n人仔試過係室內有7x mb<br />\nSMT 頂到盡真係得1x mb"},{"pid":"fa51ccb88b94d6196b2f9bbd5a4156b9ae03f5be","tid":184752,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5J3CyHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5J3CyHy.jpg&h=0d0d7760&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n450 MBPS 係CSL<br />\n數碼通邊忽有寫450MBPS<br />\n同埋你估下如果數通碼真係做到450MBPS你慌佢唔賣行廣告????<br />\n鬼國移動330MBPS都賣行廣告啦"},{"pid":"e0a5c53520bfbc8781a890b0e93ad3b39df47d91","tid":184752,"uid":68062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5J3CyHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5J3CyHy.jpg&h=0d0d7760&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n450 MBPS 係CSL<br />\n數碼通邊忽有寫450MBPS<br />\n同埋你估下如果數通碼真係做到450MBPS你慌佢唔賣行廣告????<br />\n鬼國移動330MBPS都賣行廣告啦</blockquote><br />\n可能巴打你個位收得唔好姐，我用SMT 平均都有20mb（張卡最高42mb）<br />\n而且我都只係手機用唔share wifi ,基本上有7.2mb就好夠"}]}